parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, and the recall issues can cause frustration and anxiety for vehicle owners.

airbag warning indicator is flashing

sudden acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel and propulsion system can cause accidents, injuries, and vehicle damage.

fuel system failure
sudden acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause accidents, injuries, and vehicle damage.

electrical system failure.

wipers
signals
and other electrical components; unexpected shutdown of the vehicle; unintended movement of the vehicle.

wipers
signals
and other electrical components; unexpected shutdown of the vehicle; unintended movement of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause serious injury or death in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control system can cause unintended acceleration, which can lead to accidents or loss of control of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The violent shaking of the front end can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially life-threatening situations.
symptoms: The front end of the vehicle shakes or bounces violently when driving over bumps or at high speeds
making it difficult to control the steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden lock-up of the steering wheel can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially life-threatening situations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially life-threatening situations.
symptoms: The power steering system fails
making it difficult to steer the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear drive shaft can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially life-threatening situations.
symptoms: The rear drive shaft falls out of the vehicle
causing the rear wheels to lock up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in recall repairs can cause continued risk of accidents and potentially life-threatening situations.
symptoms: The parts for recall repairs are unavailable
causing delays in fixing the safety issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear axle pinion nut can cause the driveshaft to detach from the vehicle, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injury or death.
symptoms: The driveshaft detaches from the vehicle
loud noises
shaking
and vibrations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.

the service 4WD light comes on

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TIPM can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience electrical issues, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls
the engine misfires
the check engine light comes on
the vehicle experiences electrical issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear differential can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The rear tires seize
the vehicle shakes
the rear differential makes a loud whirring sound

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front suspension and steering system can cause the vehicle to vibrate, shake, or lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates or shakes while driving
especially at high speeds; the front end of the vehicle wobbles or shakes; the steering wheel vibrates or is difficult to control; the vehicle pulls to one side while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hub assembly and bearing can cause the wheel to detach, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle emits a grinding or whining noise; the wheel vibrates or shakes; the wheel detaches from the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The ignition key locks up or is unable to turn; the turn signal flashes or operates incorrectly; the wipers operate intermittently; the cruise control surges or malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to accurately report the vehicle's mileage can lead to safety issues and affect the vehicle's reliability.
symptoms: The odometer reading is incorrect or has not rolled over.
